      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，EmptyLot作为起点。那车辆进入后的下一个状态是什么？是直接进入Full，还是中间有个过渡？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "Park vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "应该有中间状态，叫PartiallyFull，表示部分车位被占用。从EmptyLot停车后先到PartiallyFull，再停才到Full。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Park vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上了EmptyLot到PartiallyFull的转移，以及PartiallyFull到Full的转移，触发条件都是Park vehicle。同时补充了PartiallyFull的定义说明。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Park vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "离开的逻辑也要对称。Full状态Remove vehicle回到PartiallyFull，PartiallyFull再Remove vehicle就回到EmptyLot。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Full",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "EmptyLot",
        "Remove vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Full -- PartiallyFull是Remove vehicle，PartiallyFull -- EmptyLot也是Remove vehicle。这两个转移我都加上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Full",
        "PartiallyFull",
